				src=&#34;https://adamcook.io/p/deploying-hugo-websites-in-azure-for-pennies-or-free-on-github-pages/images/staticwebapp-01.jpg&#34; width=&#34;1355&#34; height=&#34;782&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
